         <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">

            <p n="1">
               Prosperity! Fortune!
            </p>

            <p n="1-3">
               Writ of the Mahārāja Nandivarman.
            </p>

            <p n="3-7">
               Let the honourable members of the assembly of Kūram know<note>Literally: "see".</note>!
            </p>

            <p n="7-14">
               Having removed the previous holders of the six <foreign>paṭṭi</foreign>s of land named <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>āyiṉa</foreign><note>Literally: "which is".</note></supplied> Akkaḷanimmaṭippoṟṟi in their village, in the twentieth year <gap reason="undefined"/>
